人<br />\n就係人地影響緊我地<br />\n我地更團結 去改變香港<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n衝得要走得快<br />\n哨兵Be Water <br />\nFirst aid 補給 <br />\n全世界只有你可以有能力保護自己同記者<br />\n有咩搵我幫手 免費教大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港需要你<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有需 要TG 唔問名 <br />\n唔會問聯絡資料<br />\n同你Case Study <br />\n教你點飲食點運動<br />\n20％運動 80％營養<br />\n學完再善用Budget 搞好自己體能<br />\n如果想做下運動放鬆<br />\n歡迎黎搵我做下運動 <br />\n有街頭健身<br />\n<br />\nMy TG<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/TreeHoIsGood\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTreeHoIsGood&d=5WD1fpiCBK613UyTU9OnXxTmJET03dBbukdTSFliYCA%3D&h=83c2556b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TreeHoIsGood</a><br />\nChannel<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/treehoHealthAdvice\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FtreehoHealthAdvice&d=5WD1fpiCBK613UyTU9OnXxTmJET03dBbukdTSFliYCA%3D&h=55772763\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/treehoHealthAdvice</a><br />\n<br />\n長期戰爭 齊上齊落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n對抗白色恐怖 <br />\n唔駛驚冇工開 <br />\n想開工/彈性part time<br />\n可以黎搵我 我cover你<br />\n反共抗中 我地勢不兩立<br />\nWe Shall Never Surrender<br />\n<br />\nUnited, We can win the fight"},{"pid":"dfb36f86429a0912eeb62b1c0c0c82c6ceb57f93","tid":1696112,"uid":85822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"380e2656270d1bb2584e0bacaa026769644aa36a","tid":1696112,"uid":206448,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T03:52:56.000Z","msg":"想知點增肥<br />\n食極唔肥體質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T13:38:36.000Z","msg":"改善好腸胃吸收先<br />\n逐樣做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b310d7ed1921dce92dfa5de5379b9a7a35e5c0fe","t